dcterms:description: A dataset containing non-Abelian gauge fields in circuit systems, which serves as a basis for investigating the properties and behaviors of non-Abelian physics.
dcterms:title: Non-Abelian Gauge Field Circuit Dataset

dcterms:description: A collection of circuit diagrams and structure information used for model training and validation.
dcterms:title: Circuit Diagrams and Structure Information

dcterms:description: A dataset consisting of 500 pairs of network predictions and corresponding theoretical results for comparison and validation.
dcterms:title: 500 Pairs of Network Predictions and Corresponding Theoretical Results

dcterms:description: A dataset containing 4,096 sets of circuit diagrams and structure information for dataset construction and model training.
dcterms:title: 4,096 Sets of Circuit Diagrams and Structure Information

dcterms:description: A collection of 500 datasets used for model validation in the context of non-Abelian gauge fields.
dcterms:title: 500 Datasets for Model Validation
